cz.cuni.mff.kocur.influence

Class FOWLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.world.GridSystem
      • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.influence.InfluenceLayer
        • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.influence.FOWLayer

  • public class FOWLayer
extends InfluenceLayer
    Layer that stores our field of view inside the influence map. It sets 1 influence to tiles that are visible. This should have been used to combine with other layers by multiplying. That would give us only a visible influence.
    Author:
    kocur
